<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN305">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>vayalaik koṭiyiṉ vāṭiya maruṅku</l>
<l>luyava lūrtip payalaip pārppā</l>
<l>ṉelli vantunil lātu pukkuc</l>
<l>colliya collō cilavē yataṟkē</l>
<l>yēṇiyuñ cīppu māṟṟi</l>
<l>māṇviṉai yāṉaiyu maṇikaḷain taṉavē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The pale brahmin on a decrepit vehicle</l>
<l>with a stomach withered like a purslane creeper,</l>
<l>at night he came [and], without stopping, entered.</l>
<l>Few were the words he spoke. Because of that</l>
<l>the changed the ladders and bolts</l>
<l>and removed the bells from the elephant of glorious work.</l>
</lg> 
    </div>
